[[Start of the Journey<-Talk to someone else]] ###THE FELLOWSHIP OF THE MOOD RING You have inherited an evil mood ring from rich Uncle Larry, who wore it to his dying day. *God bless his miserable soul!* In his will he bequeathed you with all of his wealth under the condition that you destroy the mood ring, which has been left in your possession. To do this, you must wear the ring and travel to Hawaii Island where you will climb to the top of Kilauea, an active volcano. You will toss the ring into the mouth of the volcano to destroy it. However, you will not be able to remove the ring from your finger until it is completely powerless. You will be travelling with 5 companions who will assist you in making the ring powerless. During your journey you will engage in conversations with them where your Emotional Intelligence (EI) will be tested. Each time you have a positive EI response to something a companion says you will gain one point and the color of the mood ring will change. When the point value reaches 10, the mood ring will turn pink which indicates all of its power has been drained and it can destroyed. Never to be used again! Your companions are Chaitan, Regan, Spandana, Bonar, and Alvina. Chaitan is male. He will test you on your self-awareness (SA). Regan is male. He will test your ability to self-regulate (SR). Spandana is female. She will test your motivation (M). Bonar is male. He will test your ability to show empathy (E). And finally, Alvina is female. She will test your social skills (SS). Together you are the fellowship of the mood ring! Let the journey begin...
